    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-quality E46 M3, a masterclass in atmospheric induction. Under the hood lies the S54 3.2L straight-six, producing 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual and a variable M-differential lock, providing an unfiltered analog connection. Mechanically, this example is beyond reproach: the subframe is reinforced, the rod bearings have been proactively addressed, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications. This is a zero-fault, high-performance icon for the discerning collector.",
